# Knowledge: Certifications

## Cybersecurity

| Cert | Issuer | Level | Cost | Best For |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Google Cybersecurity Certificate | Google / Coursera | Beginner | ~$50/mo (audit free) | First cert, SOC analyst jobs |
| CompTIA Security+ | CompTIA | Intermediate | ~$400 | Industry baseline, required by many employers |
| CompTIA Network+ | CompTIA | Beginner-Mid | ~$350 | Networking fundamentals before Security+ |
| CEH (Certified Ethical Hacker) | EC-Council | Intermediate | ~$1000+ | Pen testing, ethical hacking roles |
| OSCP | Offensive Security | Advanced | ~$1500 | Penetration testing, hands-on lab exam |
| eJPT | eLearnSecurity | Beginner | ~$200 | Affordable intro to pen testing |
| TryHackMe Paths | TryHackMe | All levels | Free / ~$14/mo | Learning + portfolio building |

